headline: Garmin: Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: SCHAFFHAUSEN, Switzerland (AP) — Garmin Ltd. (GRMN) on Wednesday reported second-quarter net income of $400.8 million. The Schaffhausen, Switzerland-based company said it had net income of $2.07 per share. Earnings, adjusted for one-time gains and costs, were $2.17 per share.
